plot , plot , and then more plot a very intricate , involved thriller about a special effects man , an expert in disguise , and a plan to fake the death of a mafia kingpin who is about to talk to the authorities . all kinds of double dealings are going on here ; in fact , so much story is going on with so little attention to character development that after it 's over it all quickly begins to evaporate from your memory . quickly forgettable . bill conti wrote the music , which is interesting